               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Lama‘āt by ʻIrāqī, Fakhr al-Dīn Ibrāhīm, -1289?</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85100085" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1101B-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>The Lamaʻāt (لمعات) by Fakhr al-Dīn ʻIrāqī, an exposition of Sufi doctrines in mixed prose and verse.</p>
                        <p>Seal impressions (f. 1r) dated 1010 (1601/2) and 1099 (1687/88).</p>
                        <p>116 ff.; 7 lines per page; inelegant nastaʻliq; rubrications; many marginal and interlinear notes; worm-eaten and water-stained; 16th century.</p>
                     </note>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_7901">Lama‘āt</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_7901">لمعات</title>
                     <author>
